      <description>Welcome I am a postdoctoral researcher at the University of St. Gallen. My research interests include industrial organization, competition policy, digital markets, applied econometrics, and machine learning. I am currently employed on funding obtained via the SNF research project &amp;ldquo;Pricing in a Digital World&amp;rdquo; that was proposed together with Prof. Stefan Buehler (University of St. Gallen). Prof. Thomas Epper (University of St. Gallen) and Prof. Daniel Halbheer (HEC Paris) are further project partners.</description>
